data.eml:eml: Two new species of Cumacea (Malacostraca, Peracarida) from Peter The Great Bay (Sea of Japan)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tzareva, Ludmila, Vassilenko, Stella (2006): Two new species of Cumacea (Malacostraca, Peracarida) from Peter The Great Bay (Sea of Japan). Zootaxa 1174: 41-48, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.2645802
